re-than-just-sun-its-a-business-mecca%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGold%20Coast%20in%20Australia%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'd%20been%20living%20overseas%2C%20then%20in%20Melbourne%20and%20regional%20Victoria%20for%2015%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20trip%20to%20see%20my%20folks%20last%20July%2C%20I%20noticed%20how%20much%20their%20health%20was%20declining%20and%20realized%20that%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-back-hometown-closer-parents-grandparents-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etime%20with%20my%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20running%20out.%20It%20was%20now%20or%20never%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20live%20close%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gold%20Coast's%20property%20and%20rental%20prices%20have%20skyrocketed%20in%20recent%20years.%20And%20so%2C%20when%20my%20parents%20offered%20us%20their%20home%20while%20they%20traveled%20through%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%20for%20two%20months%2C%20we%20leapt%20at%20the%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20back%20into%20mum%20and%20dad's%20house%20%E2%80%94%20the%20one%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20until%20I%20went%20to%20university%20at%2017%20%E2%80%94%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20how%20it%20would%20go.%20Would%20I%20feel%20like%20a%20failure%20returning%20to%20the%20nest%20after%20so%20many%20years%20away%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWas%20I%20actually%20going%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-gen-z-living-parents-home-boomerang-kids-wealth-divide-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboomerang%20kid%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20an%20adult%20who%20returns%20to%20live%20at%20the%20family%20home%20because%20they%20can't%20stand%20on%20their%20own%20two%20feet%20financially%3F%20Yep%2C%20I'm%20afraid%20I%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20one%20January%20morning%2C%20my%20parents%20flew%20to%20America%2C%20and%20later%20that%20afternoon%2C%20our%20family%20of%20five%20rolled%20into%20their%20driveway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20little%2