0liked%20it.%20I%20liked%20hearing%20stories%20and%20questioning%20their%20particulars%3B%20I%20liked%20my%20classmates%20and%20the%20intellectual%20freedom%20we%20could%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20debating%20whether%20Simone%20de%20Beauvoir%20is%20being%20overly%20dismissive%20of%20Rosa%20Luxemburg%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Second%20Sex%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20if%20I%20find%20the%20Consort%20Yang%20scandal%20a%20satisfactory%20explanation%20for%20the%20An%20Lushan%20rebellion%20during%20the%20Tang%20Dynasty.%20Also%2C%20no%2C%20I%20still%20don't%20understand%20the%20Balkans%20since%201453.%20I'm%20convinced%20nobody%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENever%20did%20I%20think%20those%20revelations%20would%20get%20me%20a%20job%20immediately%20after%20college%2C%20but%20I%20believed%20my%20skills%20would%20be%20transferable%20to%20a%20number%20of%20careers.%20I%20became%20an%20expert%20in%20writing%2C%20research%2C%20and%20critical%20thinking.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20needs%20writers%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20classic%20refrain%20I%20heard%20in%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-jobs-college-finance-clubs-admissions-process-cutthroat-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eupperclassman%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20since%20graduation%2C%20I've%20tried%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20write%20professionally%2C%20from%20content%20writer%20to%20copywriter%20to%20media%20jobs%2C%20but%20it%20always%20feels%20like%20I'm%20one%20step%20behind%20the%20curve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20far%20the%20most%20common%20job%20posting%20now%20is%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhottest-job-in-tech-writing-words-ai-hiring-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20content%20writer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20someone%20who%20reviews%20and%20improves%20the%20responses%20of%20generative%20AI.%20That%20was%20not%20what%20I%20studied%20to%20do.%20I%20fear%20AI%2C%20along%20with%20concerning%20trends%20in%20media%20and%20research%20in%20general%2C%20may%20be%20freezing%20humanities%20majors%20out%20of%20the%20job%20market%20exactly%20when%20the%20ever-artificial%20world%20needs%20some%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2248fa0d63-1b63-4e13-9e8d-56da6213109e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20struggled%20to%20picture%20my%20future%20throughout%20college%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20never%20sure%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20for%20a%20career.%20I%20thought%20about%20becoming%20a%20writer%2C%20I%20thought%20about%20becoming%20a%20teacher%2C%20I%20thought%20about%20going%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgraduate-school-masters-mba-college-regret-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egraduate%20school%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Write%20what%3F%20Teach%20what%3F%20Go%20where%3F%20These%20are%20questions%20I%20didn't%20have%20answers%20for%20yet%2C%20and%20I%20was%20sure%20that%20was%20fine%20because%20I%20was%20only%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20life%20came%20at%20me%20fast%2C%20and%20the%20steps%20to%20success%20came%20barrelling%20down%20the%20road%20like%20a%20truck%20with%20no%20brakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20I%20liked%20writing%2C%20and%20I%20could%20imagine%20myself%20in%20both%20academic%20and%20journalism%20careers%2C%20so%20in%20college%2C%20I%20began%20writing%20about%20the%20Boston%20Celtics%20for%20several%20websites.%20I%20eventually%20started%20writing%20about%20various%20sports.%20It%20was%20fulfilling%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20nearly%20enough%20to%20be%20called%20an%20internship%3B%20those%20writing%20gigs%20were%20never%20going%20to%20turn%20into%20full-time%20offers%20after%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20my%20academic%20pursuits%2C%20namely%20my%20senior%20honors%20thesis%2C%20was%20going%20to%20come%20with%20one%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oliver%20Fox%20holding%20up%20his%20senior%20thesis%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8b081fd4fbd083f298b82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20with%20his%20senior%20thesis.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Oliver%20Fox%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20it%20was%20my%20fault%20for%20studying%20history%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20I%20was%20still%20a%20teenager%20when%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteach-same-college-earned-bachelors-weird-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeclared%20my%20major%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20about%20as%20useful%20as%20one%20in%20today's%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20now%20left%20wondering%20if%20my%20degree%20will%20help%20me%20get%20a%20job%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22479a8f72-bd82-4a9c-a92a-2e7d3df27d90%5C%22%3EI%20can't%20find%20a%20job%20in%20today's%20artificially%20intelligent%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EQualified%20to%20do%20exactly%20two%20things%20%E2%80%94%20write%20about%20sports%20and%20do%20historical%20research%20%E2%80%94%20the%20world%20of%20LinkedIn%2C%20Indeed%2C%20job%20boards%2C%20and%20career%20center%20events%20has%20felt%20like%20a%20barrage%20of%20distillation.%20I%20need%20to%20explain%20to%20the%20market%20why%20I'm%20useful%2C%20even%20though%20I'm%20hardly%20convinced%20of%20it%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESports%20media%20is%20hemorrhaging%20full-time%20jobs%2C%20and%20the%20Trump%20Administration%20is%20gutting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-research-funding-cuts-nobel-prizes-brain-drain-medicine-ai-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacademic%20research%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Graduate%20school%20funding%20froze%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20now%20face%20the%20endless%20scrolling%20through%20jobs%20for%20%26quot%3Bwriters%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bresearchers%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20my%20only%20options%20seem%20to%20be%20a%20slew%20of%20AI%20training%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudying%20history%2C%20I%20was%20enco