w%2F129096484.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129096484.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPriyanka%20Chopra%20and%20Nick%20Jonas%20welcomed%20their%20daughter%20Malti%20Marie%20Chopra%20Jonas%20in%202022%2C%20who%20was%20born%20prematurely%20at%2027%20weeks.%20The%20couple%20faced%20a%20challenging%20period%20with%20Malti%20spending%20months%20in%20the%20NICU.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20spent%202%20summers%20testing%20out%20living%20in%20different%20European%20countries.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20we're%20happily%20settled%20in%20our%20top%20pick.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20people%20in%20sunglasses%20smiling%20in%20front%20of%20water%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8a5941fb3fcb42648ef35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20searched%20Europe%20for%20a%20new%20home%20and%20eventually%20settled%20on%20our%20top%20pick%20and%20made%20the%20move.%20%3Cp%3EAshley%20Stahm%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20left%20the%20US%20to%20spend%20several%20months%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20place%20in%20Europe%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20call%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOur%20ideal%20home%20would%20be%20walkable%2C%20have%20accessible%20healthcare%20and%20visa%20options%2C%20and%20feel%20diverse.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20visiting%20several%20countries%20and%20cities%2C%20we%20found%20ourselves%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-living-in-lisbon-work-life-balance-expat-2023-8%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoving%20to%20Lisbon%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Portugal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20really%20tells%20you%20how%20to%20look%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehome%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20don't%20mean%20a%20structure%20with%20four%20walls%20and%20a%20front%20door.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20mean%20the%20place%20you're%20proud%20to%20be%20part%20of%2C%20to%20describe%20to%20people%20who've%20never%20been%2C%20to%20bond%20over%20with%20strangers%20you've%20just%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20honest%2C%20my%20husband%20Cody%20and%20I%20started%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fwhat-to-look-for-when-buying-a-house%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esearch%20for%20a%20new%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20vastly%20different%20perspectives%3A%20I'm%20a%20Guyanese-American%20Black%20woman%20raised%20by%20Caribbean%20parents%20in%20an%20eclectic%20corner%20of%20North%20Jersey.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20proudly%20wearing%20my%20badge%20of%20independence%20as%20I%20took%20the%20bus%20and%20train%20between%20my%20hometown%20and%20New%20York%20City%2C%20the%20sound%20of%20different%20languages%20lulling%20me%20to%20sleep%20on%20the%20way%20home%20from%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECody%2C%20the%20firstborn%20in%20a%20blended%2C%20mostly%20evangelical%20family%2C%20jumped%20at%20the%20chance%20to%20leave%20rural%20Indiana%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20was%20able.%20He%20craved%20walkability%2C%20third%20spaces%2C%20and%20access%20to%20culturally%20diverse%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20met%20nearly%2012%20years%20ago%20in%20North%20Carolina%20and%2C%20for%20a%20while%2C%20found%20some%20common%20ground%20in%20Durham%20%E2%80%94%20its%20tight-knit%20community%20felt%20familiar%20to%20me%2C%20and%20the%20(semi)%20walkable%20neighborhoods%20suited%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20remote%20companies%20became%20our%20sole%20source%20of%20work%2C%20we%20found%20ourselves%20with%20the%20freedom%20and%20opportunity%20to%20do%20what%20we%20hadn't%20before%3A%20travel%20overseas.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20we%20began%20to%20wonder%20if%20home%20might%20exist%20outside%20the%20contiguous%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22adab3af5-8374-4d28-b03f-df0a75178bb0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThroughout%20our%20summer%20of%20travel%2C%20we%20began%20looking%20for%20a%20place%20to%20settle%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221537%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20in%20London%20smiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8a6261fb3fcb42648ef57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221153%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELondon%3Cp%3EAshley%20Stahm%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe'd%20never%20been%20to%20Europe%2C%20so%20we%20took%20two%20months%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202023%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flast-minute-trip-to-france-best-things-what-change-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravel%20to%20Paris%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nice%2C%20and%20Cassis%2C%20France%3B%20Brussels%2C%20Belgium%3B%20Amsterdam%2C%20Netherlands%3B%20and%20London%2C%20England.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20cities%2C%20of%20course%2C%20are%20as%20different%20as%20the%20four%20corners%20of%20the%20US%2C%20and%20perhaps%20even%20more%20so%20due%20to%20linguistic%2C%20cultural%2C%20and%20climate%20differences.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20packed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-i-always-check-bag-when-flying-seasoned-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esingle%20checked%20bag%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20hauled%20it%20from%20city%20to%20city%20on%20trains%20and%20across%20cobblestones%2C%20shedding%20our%20crewnecks%20and%20rain%20jackets%20as%20we%20walked%20along%20Amsterdam's%20canals%20for%20shorts%20and%20bathing%20suits%20in%20the%20south%20of%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20loved%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-netherlands-mistakes-to-avoid-from-local%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebicycle%20infrastructure%20in%20Amsterdam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20culture%20in%20Paris%2C%20and%20the%20cultural%20diversity%20and%20ample%20green%20space%20in%20London.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20our%20research%20taught%20us%20that%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20France%2C%20and%20the%20UK%20would%20not%20be%20particularly%20easy%20countries%20for%20us%20to%20immigrate%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20to%20mention%2C%20we%20stayed%20in%20each%20city%20during%20the%20summer%2C%20experiencing%20the%20most%20vibrant%20version%20of%20each.%20What%20would%20living%20in%20London%20feel%20like%20in%20winter%2C%20with%20the%20sun%20lost%20behind%20endless%20overcast%20skies%3F%20What%20would%20Paris%20be%20like%20when%20it%20rained%20days%20on%20end%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221537%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20with%20bicycle%20near%20bridge%2C%20flowers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8a6391fb3fcb42648ef5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221153%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmsterdam%3Cp%3EAshley%20Stahm%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20six%20weeks%20into%20our%20foray%20across%20those%20four%20countries%20that%20summer%2C%20we%20took%20a%20beat.%20What%2C%20exactly%2C%20were%20we%20looking%20for%3F%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'd%20seen%20Big%20Ben.%20We'd%20seen%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower.%20We'd%20biked%20across%20canals%20in%20Amsterdam%2C%20and%20had%20Belgian%20waffles%20in%20the%20place%20they%20originated%20because%2C%20well%2C%20of%20course%20we%20did.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20magic%20of%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-mistakes-europe-trip-multiple-countries-packing-planning-saving-money-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst%20European%20tour%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20captivating%2C%20sure%2C%20but%20we%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehome.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20realigned%20on%20the%20basics%3A%20We%20specifically%20wanted%20a%20place%20where%20we%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeing-childfree-gave-me-capacity-for-different-types-of-friendships-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuild%20a%20childfree%20community%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20craved%20places%20for%20adults%20to%20meet%20and%20support%20one%20another%2C%20with%20the%20intent%20of%20growing%20old%20together.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20never%2C%20ever%20wanted%20to%20own%20a%20car%20again.%20We%20wanted%20healthcare%20to%20feel%20accessible.%20We%20needed%20a%20feasible%20way%20to%20immigrate%20and%20integrate%2C%20language%2C%20bureaucracy%2C%20and%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20wanted%20to%20be%20in%20this%20new%20home%20for%20the%20long%20haul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294be6a56-1751-4f90-bc54-94d3692cee40%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20our%20travels%20continued%2C%20we%20found%20a%20not-so-great%20fit%20and%20one%20city%20that%20felt%20right%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20and%20woman%20toasting%20drinks%20at%20table%2C%20smiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8a5d71fb3fcb42648ef46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20spent%20our%20travels%20exploring%20new%20places%20and%20celebrating%20milestones.%20%3Cp%3EAshley%20Stahm%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20with%20that%20renewed%20direction%20that%20we%20went%20home%20and%20planned%20for%20our%20next%20trip%20across%20the%20Atlantic%3A%20this%20time%20to%20Lisbon%2C%20Portugal%2C%20and%20Barcelona%2C%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20their%20two%20countries%20shared%20a%20border%2C%20these%20two%20cities%20couldn't%20have%20been%20more%20different%20to%20us.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Barcelona%2C%20Catalan%20was%20spoken%20so%20widely%20that%20my%20high-school%20Spanish%20wasn't%20as%20useful%20as%20I'd%20hoped.%20Between%20the%20stifling%20summer%20heat%20and%20what%20I%20perceived%20as%20a%20noticeable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjohn-leguizamo-hollywood-latino-representation-cultural-apartheid-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elack%20of%20visible%20representation%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20dark-skinned%20Black%20(and%20Afro-Caribbean)%20women%20like%20myself%2C%20the%20city%20just%20wasn't%20a%20match%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20expecting%20to%20see%20reflections%20of%20myself%20everywhere%3B%20I%20was%20in%20Europe%2C%20after%20all.%20However%2C%20knowing%20that%20Spain%20is%20home%20to%20millions%20of%20immigrants%2C%20I%20also%20hadn't%20expected%20to%20feel%20so%20conspicuous%20and%20be%20pored%20over%20so%20much.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20left%20Spain%20feeling%20more%20alienated%20than%20ever%2C%20Portugal%20soon%20stole%20our%20hearts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverywhere%20I%20looked%2C%20I%20saw%20melanin.%20Throughout%20our%20time%20in%20Lisbon%2C%20I%20heard%20a%20mix%20of%20languages%20and%20accents%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20European%20Portuguese%2C%20but%20also%20Brazilian%2C%20Angolan%2C%20and%20Mozambican%20Portuguese%2C%20along%20with%20French%20and%20English%20%E2%80%94%20reflecting%20the%20diversity%20of%20the%20people%20around%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sat%20among%20greenery%2C%20quiosques%2C%20miradouros%2C%20and%20old%20ladies%20in%20crisp%20slacks%20with%20beers%20in%20hand%20at%2011%20a.m.%2C%20gossiping%20with%20their%20neighbors%20before%20heading%20to%20the%20local%20tasca%20for%20almo%C3%A7o%20and%20a%20pastel%20de%20nata.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20us%2C%20Lisbon%20felt%20like%20it%20could%20be%20home.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227320a617-54ba-4b01-ba5c-2a5258f09662%5C%22%3EAfter%202%20years%20of%20searching%2C%20we've%20settled%20on%20Lisbon%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20smiling%20against%20colorful%20door%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8acab1fb3fcb42648f03a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrom%20the%20north%20in%20Porto%20to%20the%20south%20in%20the%20Algarve%2C%20I%20couldn't%20pick%20my%20jaw%20up%20off%20the%20floor.%3Cp%3EAshley%20Stahm%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-visiting-portugal-first-time-from-local-tour-guide-lisbon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPortugal's%20capital%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20we%20had%20found%20walkable%20neighborhoods%20and%20a%20social%20community%20of%20both%20locals%20and%20expats%20%E2%80%94%20just%20as%20we'd%20hoped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20warm%20and%20sunny%20year-round%2C%20so%20we%20didn't%20need%20to%20worry%20so%20much%20about%20possible%20gloominess%20during%20other%20seasons.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortugal%20also%20offers%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-single-payer-healthcare-is-like-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Euniversal%20public%20healthcare%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20seems%20accessible%2C%20plus%20more%20visa%20routes%20than%20some%20other%20countries%20we'd%20considered.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20truly%20multicultural%20countries%2C%20though%2C%20it%20is%20grappling%20with%20geopolitical%20and%20economic%20friction%20that%20we're%20still%20learning%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20what%20was%20on%20our%20list%2C%20and%20then%20there%20was%20what%20our%20hearts%20needed%3A%20A%20country%20willing%20to%20welcome%20us%2C%20teach%20us%2C%20and%20be%20patient%20(as%20we%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-became-us-citizen-through-naturalization-h1b-visa-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efile%20our%20immigration%20paperwork%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20language%20we're%20still%20learning).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20immigrants%20in%20a%20land%20whose%20respect%20we%20are%20still%20earning%2C%20alongside%20fr