_blank%5C%22%3EGriffin%20Johnson%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-in-nyc-moving-from-midwest-differences-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20farm%20in%20the%20Midwes%3C%2Fa%3Et.%20Like%20a%20lot%20of%20farm%20kids%2C%20I%20was%20around%20horses%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20know%20anything%20about%20the%20sport%20of%20horse%20racing.%20My%20dad%20is%20a%20factory%20worker%2C%20and%20my%20mom's%20a%20nurse.%20They%20raised%20our%20family%20on%20about%20%2460%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20and%20we%20had%20no%20financial%20literacy.%20From%20the%20horses%20themselves%20to%20the%20fancy%20outfits%20at%20the%20Kentucky%20Derby%2C%20everything%20about%20racing%20felt%20unattainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20enrolled%20in%20college%2C%20planning%20to%20become%20a%20nurse%2C%20like%20my%20mom.%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fposting-social-media-to-get-a-job-boost-confidence-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eposting%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20showing%20snapshots%20of%20my%20day%20as%20a%20male%20nursing%20student.%20I%20was%20an%20early%20adopter%20on%20TikTok%2C%20and%20my%20posts%20took%20off.%20The%20pandemic%20TikTok%20craze%20really%20benefited%20me.%20Today%20I%20have%209.6%20million%20followers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40imgriffinjohnson%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%202.6%20million%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fimgriffinjohnson%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20about%2067%2C000%20followers%20on%20Facebook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20determined%20to%20leverage%20that%20following%20into%20something%20even%20more%20substantial%20and%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222bbe8955-3e90-41e8-81c4-05cd8286853d%5C%22%3EI%20used%20social%20media%20to%20get%20ownership%20of%20my%20first%20horse%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20finished%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-being-a-nurse-has-changed-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enursing%20degree%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021.%20Yet%2C%20by%20then%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20had%20something%20much%20more%20valuable%20on%20hand%3A%20an%20audience.%20In%202021%2C%20I%20started%20Animal%20Capital%2C%20a%20firm%20that%20helps%20brands%20connect%20with%20their%20target%20customers%20through%20influencer%20and%20celebrity%20partnerships.%20I%20didn't%20bring%20cash%20to%20the%20enterprise%2C%20but%20was%20able%20to%20leverage%20my%20audience%20to%20attract%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20cofounder%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-kentucky-derby-can-cost-millions-kentucky-derby-horse-race-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvolved%20with%20horse%20racing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20saw%20how%20the%20horse%20racing%20industry%20could%20benefit%20from%20partnerships%20like%20those%20we%20were%20pursuing%20at%20Animal%20Capital.%20He%20connected%20me%20with%20West%20Point%20Thoroughbreds%2C%20which%20owns%20many%20horses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Griffin%20Johnson%20riding%20horse%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f0783e8408f66718038d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22968%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGriffin%20Johnson%20knew%20nothing%20about%20horse%20racing%20before%20buying%20a%20stake%20in%20a%20horse.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Griffin%20Johnson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20reached%20a%20deal%3A%20I%20would%20take%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frace-horse-euthanized-after-injury-hours-before-preakness-stakes-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E2.5%25%20stake%20in%20a%20racehorse%3C%2Fa%3E%20named%20Sandman.%20In%20exchange%2C%20I%20would%20post%20about%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20be%20an%20owner.%20There%20wasn't%20a%20formal%20number%20of%20posts%20required.%20By%20that%20point%2C%20I%20had%20learned%20a%20bit%20about%20horse%20racing%20and%20just%20wanted%20to%20post%20for%20the%20love%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254f345bf-d4d5-4652-b6b8-0ddc0ca4e837%5C%22%3EI've%20won%20about%20%2425%2C000%20from%20that%20horse%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20got%20into%20horse%20racing%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20stop.%20I%20now%20own%20equity%20in%20four%20horses%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20a%20partner%20at%20West%20Point%20Thoroughbreds%20since%202024.%20I%20love%20the%20competition%2C%20and%20feeling%20like%20I'm%20part%20of%20a%20team%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20how%20I%20imagine%20it%20feels%20to%20be%20involved%20with%20Formula%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20unique%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fviral-crying-horse-plushie-symbol-chinese-corporate-hustle-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebond%20between%20humans%20and%20horses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20like%20we%20evolved%20together.%20I%20ride%20casually%2C%20though%20not%20the%20thoroughbreds%20that%20I%20own.%20Still%2C%20I%20spent%20about%2090%20days%20in%20the%20barn%20last%20year%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20connection%20that%20comes%20from%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jockey%20riding%20horse%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f06d51fb3fcb4264869cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22968%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGriffin%20Johnson%20owns%202.5%25%20stake%20in%20Sandman.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Griffin%20Johnson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20there's%20also%20money.%20Sandman%20won%20the%20Arkansas%20Derby%2C%20which%20paid%20%241.5%20million.%20From%20that%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnope-black-jockey-pictures-muybridge-horse-in-motion-history-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20jockeys%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20trainers%2C%20and%20other%20staff%20are%20paid.%20I%20made%20about%20%2420%2C000%20for%20my%202.5%25%20ownership%20stake.%20Overall%2C%20I've%20made%20about%20%2425%2C000%20total%20from%20owning%20Sandman%20and%20have%20won%20smaller%20amounts%20from%20my%20other%20horses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6d21ac8-ac4a-4582-b1e0-1246fcd40187%5C%22%3EI've%20been%20able%20to%20network%20with%20other%20owners%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20learned%20that%20horse%20racing%20isn't%20just%20for%20old%20rich%20guys.%20That's%20part%20of%20my%20work%20%E2%80%94%20to%20show%20that%20this%20sport%20is%20more%20accessible%20than%20people%20might%20think.%20People%20without%20much%20wealth%20can%20buy%20small%20stakes%20in%20their%20favorite%20racehorses%2C%20much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-investing-strategy-buy-the-dip-dollar-cost-average-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elike%20buying%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Even%20fancy%20tracks%2C%20like%20Churchill%20Downs%20(home%20of%20the%20Kentucky%20Derby)%2C%20do%20%242%20beer%20nights%2C%20which%20is%20just%20a%20fun%20environment%20to%20be%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20at%20the%20track%20on%20race%20days%2C%20the%20crowd%20is%20so%20diverse.%20Some%20people%20have%20never%20set%20foot%20on%20a%20college%20campus%2C%20but%20they%20know%20everything%20there%20is%20to%20know%20about%20horses.%20Others%20are%20business%20people%20who%20have%20made%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20common%20interest%20with%20those%20people%20has%20allowed%20me%20to%20expand%20my%20network%20and%20access%20amazing%20mentorship.%20One%20of%20Sandman's%20other%20owners%20is%20Vinnie%20Viola%2C%20a%20billionaire%20and%20owner%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-panthers-fire-gerard-gallant-make-him-wait-for-taxi-2016-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFlorida%20Panthers%20NHL%20team%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%2026%20years%20old%20and%20have%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20ask%20him%20for%20advice.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20race%20day%2C%20some%20of%20the%20wealthiest%20and%20most%20successful%20people%20in%20the%20world%20come%20together%20in%20one%20spot%2C%20and%20being%20an%20owner%20gives%20me%20a%20ticket%20to%20join%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-media-influencer-racehorse-ownership-kentucky-derby-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772719801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f03911fb3fcb426486986%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-media-influencer-racehorse-ownership-kentucky-derby-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20turned%20my%20TikTok%20following%20into%20equity%20in%20a%20racehorse%2C%20earning%20%2425%2C000%20and%20networking%20with%20billionaires.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-media-influencer-racehorse-ownership-kentucky-derby-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Europe%E2%80%99s%20Animation%20Industry%20Honors%20%E2%80%98Last%20Whale%20Singer%2C%E2%80%99%20Les%20Films%20du%20Pr%C3%A9au%2C%20%E2%80%98Allah%20Is%20Not%20Obliged%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Acorn%E2%80%99s%20Adventure%E2%80%99%20at%20Cartoon%20Movie%202026%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772719739000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236680163%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22European%20animation%20celebrated%20its%20latest%20achievements%20at%20Cartoon%20Movie%2C%20the%20must-attend%20pitching%20and%20co-production%20forum%20for%20European%20animated%20features%20which%20concludes%20today%20in%20Bordeaux.%20Voted%20by%20industry%20pr