3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmong%20the%20sandwiches%20from%20McDonald's%2C%20Burger%20King%2C%20Wendy's%2C%20Popeyes%2C%20and%20Bojangles%2C%20one%20stood%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBojangles%2C%20which%20just%20opened%20a%20new%20location%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20impressed%20me%20with%20its%20crispy%20filet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFast-food%20chicken%20sandwiches%20may%20look%20similar%20on%20the%20surface%2C%20but%20not%20all%20sandwiches%20deliver%20the%20same%20crunch%2C%20flavor%2C%20or%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-double-cheeseburgers-ranked-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20popular%20chains%20compare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20ordered%20chicken%20sandwiches%20from%20McDonald's%2C%20Burger%20King%2C%20Wendy's%2C%20Popeyes%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbojangles-new-york-city-review-chicken-tenders-sandwich-breakfast-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBojangles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20compared%20them%20based%20on%20taste%2C%20texture%2C%20toppings%2C%20and%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20classic%20Southern%20flavor%20profiles%20to%20more%20flaky%20filets%2C%20each%20sandwich%20brought%20something%20different%20to%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20the%20five%20chicken%20sandwiches%20ranked%20from%20worst%20to%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMcDonald's%20delivered%20a%20classic%20chicken%20sandwich%20without%20much%20fanfare.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcdonalds%20chicken%20sandwich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698cec9be1ba468a96abe2bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20crispy%20chicken%20sandwich%2C%20aptly%20named%20the%20McCrispy%2C%20was%20released%20amid%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-chick-fil-a-in-2021-chicken-sandwich-war-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E2021%20chicken%20sandwich%20wars%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20available%20in%20classic%2C%20spicy%2C%20and%20%E2%80%94%20as%20of%20January%2027%20%E2%80%94%20a%20new%2C%20limited-edition%20hot-honey%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20cost%20%247.69%2C%20excluding%20tax%2C%20at%20my%20local%20chain%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20sandwich%20comes%20with%20a%20large%20chicken%20filet%2C%20two%20pickles%2C%20and%20mayonnaise.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcdonalds%20chicken%20sandwich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698cec8fa645d11881892b1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20opened%20it%2C%20I%20noticed%20the%20sandwich%20had%20a%20very%20light%20smattering%20of%20mayonnaise.%20As%20someone%20who%20loves%20condiments%2C%20this%20was%20a%20little%20disappointing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20eager%20to%20see%20how%20it%20would%20affect%20the%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20chicken%20sandwich%20was%20juicy%20enough%20without%20the%20excess%20mayonnaise%2C%20but%20it%20lacked%20the%20distinct%20crunch%20I%20was%20looking%20for.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcdonalds%20chicken%20sandwich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698ceca7a645d11881892b21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sandwich%20was%20moist%20but%20almost%20soggy.%20The%20bun%20tasted%20pretty%20artificial%20but%20held%20the%20sandwich's%20contents%20together%20perfectly%2C%20and%20in%20terms%20of%20size%2C%20I%20thought%20McDonald's%20nailed%20the%20bun-to-chicken%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20order%20it%20again%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20blow%20me%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWendy's%20served%20up%20my%20second-least%20favorite%20chicken%20sandwich.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22wendys%20classic%20chicken%20sandwich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a750ddd3e2f1aef369ed7e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20came%20wrapped%20in%20paper%20and%20cost%20%248.99%2C%20excluding%20tax%2C%20at%20my%20local%20Wendy's%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20came%20topped%20with%20lettuce%2C%20tomato%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20mayonnaise.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22wendys%20classic%20chicken%20sandwich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a750b61fb3fcb42648db4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lettuce%20looked%20a%20little%20limp%20on%20first%20inspection%2C%20and%20there%20also%20wasn't%20much%20of%20it.%20However%2C%20the%20chicken%20filet%20was%20large%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20practically%20spilling%20out%20of%20the%20bun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUnfortunately%2C%20this%20chicken%20sandwich%20was%20underwhelming.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22wendys%20classic%20chicken%20sandwich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a750ea1fb3fcb42648db59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20sandwich%20impressed%20me%20in%20terms%20of%20size%2C%20the%20texture%20of%20the%20chicken%20filet%20let%20it%20