es.%3Cp%3ELisa%20Galek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20slightly%20annoying%20because%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20had%20to%20take%20turns%20charging%20our%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20crew%20confiscated%20one%20of%20our%20power%20strips.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223547%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22outlet%20with%20plug%20in%20it%20carnival%20legend%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63988c6d06e8f00019b8ae69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222654%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20room%20had%20one%20outlet%2C%20which%20is%20common%20in%20cruise%20cabins.%3Cp%3ELisa%20Galek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20packed%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-a-cruise-ship-employee-always-brings-with-her-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epower%20strips%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20avoid%20having%20to%20take%20turns%20using%20the%20outlet%2C%20but%20only%20one%20made%20it%20on%20board.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20crew%20confiscated%20the%20other%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarnival's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.carnival.com%2Fapp%2Fanswers%2Fdetail%2Fa_id%2F2822%2F~%2Felectric-outlets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20power%20strips%20without%20surge%20protectors%20are%20allowed%2C%20but%20ones%20that%20the%20crew%20deems%20hazardous%20will%20be%20removed%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20owner%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20cruise%20before%20disembarkation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20kids%20had%20no%20issues%20bringing%20their%20power%20strip%20into%20their%20cabin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20TV%20screen%20was%20so%20small%20that%20my%20eyes%20felt%20strained%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trip.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223773%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tv%20screen%20carnival%20legend%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63988c1a06e8f00019b8ae53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222830%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TV%20screen%20was%20too%20small.%3Cp%3ELisa%20Galek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20too-small%20TV%20screen%20is%20no%20big%20deal%20if%20you're%20not%20a%20movie%20watcher.%20However%2C%20our%20family%20likes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-for-parents-to-have-fun-on-family-cruises-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewind%20down%20by%20watching%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20week%2C%20the%20tiny%20screen%20was%20straining%20my%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EInside%20a%20table%20was%20a%20minifridge%20big%20enough%20to%20hold%20two%20bottles%20of%20wine%20and%20a%20few%20snacks.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mini%20fridge%20on%20carnival%20legend%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F639786fd764777001929d6e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20mini%20fridge%20didn't%20keep%20our%20drinks%20and%20food%20as%20cold%20as%20I'd%20prefer%20them%20to%20be.%3Cp%3ELisa%20Galek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20downside%20was%20that%20our%20fridge%20didn't%20get%20quite%20cold%20enough%20to%20chill%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20rooms%20had%20thermostats%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20they%20worked%20well.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222810%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22thermostat%20in%20carnival%20legend%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63988bf6a3bebb0018b431b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222107%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20able%20to%20control%20the%20temperature%2C%20but%20the%20thermostat%20didn't%20work%20well.%3Cp%3ELisa%20Galek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rooms%20had%20thermostats%20with%20moving%20dials%2C%20but%20turning%20them%20didn't%20seem%20to