t%2C%20Gridwise%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-uber-upfront-pricing-could-be-key-to-business-turnaround-2025-6%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eride-hailing%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20increased%20the%20share%20they%20take%20of%20each%20fare%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECatching%20a%20ride%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedical-student-shares-uber-lyft-side-hustle-gig-work-struggles-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUber%20or%20Lyft%3C%2Fa%3E%20got%20more%20expensive%20last%20year%2C%20and%20some%20riders%20are%20cutting%20back%20as%20a%20result%2C%20new%20data%20and%20a%20survey%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prices%20that%20customers%20paid%20on%20these%20apps%20rose%209.6%25%20in%202025%2C%20according%20to%20an%20annual%20report%20on%20gig%20mobility%20from%20data%20analytics%20company%20Gridwise.%20The%20report%20analyzed%20information%20about%201%20billion%20tasks%20over%20the%20past%20year%20on%20apps%20for%20ride-hailing%2C%20delivery%2C%20and%20other%20kinds%20of%20gig%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20found%20that%20the%20average%20ride%20price%20rose%20to%20%2423.66%20at%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20up%20from%20%2421.58%20in%20December%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20same%20period%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudy-comparing-uber-lyft-prices-worth-it-few-check-apps-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eride-hailing%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E%20surveyed%20%E2%80%94%2060.4%25%20%E2%80%94%20told%20Gridwise%20that%20they've%20reduced%20their%20usage%20of%20the%20apps%20due%20to%20price.%20That's%20a%20jump%20of%2016.6%20percentage%20points%20over%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20conducted%20two%20surveys%2C%20one%20in%20December%202024%20and%20the%20other%20in%20January%202026.%20Each%20asked%201%2C000%20ride-hailing%20and%20delivery%20customers%20about%20their%20app%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20belt-tightening%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehasn't%20translated%20into%20financial%20trouble%20for%20Uber%20and%20Lyft.%20They%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehave%20been%20able%20to%20keep%20growing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20turn%20a%20profit%20%E2%80%94%20by%20expanding%20their%20businesses%20to%20new%20markets.%20Uber%20has%20said%20that%20it's%20growing%20its%20ride-hailing%20and%20delivery%20operations%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-eats-partners-costco-suburbs-expansion-deliveries-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eless-dense%20suburbs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20instance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20stating%20that%20they%20are%20sensitive%20to%20prices%2C%20but%20we're%20seeing%20growth%20in%20the%20industry%20overall%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20Green%2C%20CEO%20of%20Gridwise%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20many%20consumers%20have%20been%20cutting%20back%20their%20use%20of%20ride-hailing%20apps%20and%20other%20app-based%20services%2C%20such%20as%20Airbnb%2C%20which%20grew%20out%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20built%20customer%20bases%20with%20loss-inducing%20discounts%20%E2%80%94%20colloquially%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-subsidy-uber-airbnb-prices-surge-pricing-dynamic-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emillennial%20life%20subsidy%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20fast%20ride-hailing%20prices%20increased%20depended%20on%20which%20app%20riders%20used.%20On%20average%2C%20Lyft%20priced%20its%20rides%20about%2014%25%20below%20Uber's%2C%20according%20to%20Gridwise's%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-driver-quit-full-time-job-working-60-hours-week-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egig-work%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%20behind%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethose%20rides%20saw%20their%20earnings%20rise%2C%20though%20not%20nearly%20as%20fast%20as%20fares%3A%20Gridwise%20found%20that%20gross%20driver%20pay%20increased%20by%203.6%25%20per%20trip%20and%204.1%25%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERide-hailing%20customers%20also%20took%20more%20trips%20using%20premium%20services%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-drivers-starting-own-ride-businesses-as-earnings-drop-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eblack-car%20rides%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20XL%2C%20which%20pairs%20riders%20with%20SUVs%20and%20other%20large%20cars%2C%20Gridwise%20found.%20Those%20kinds%20of%20trips%20tend%20to%20cost%20more%20than%20standard%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20rides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20also%20took%20a%20bigger%20share%20of%20each%20fare%20on%20average%20in%202025.%20Average%20platform%20fees%20per%20trip%20rose%20about%2033%25%20in%202025%2C%20Gridwise%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Uber%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20Gridwise's%20report%20%26quot%3Brelies%20on%20a%20very%20small%20fraction%20of%20drivers%20and%20delivery%20workers%2C%20and%20doesn't%20accurately%20reflect%20the%20facts.%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fuber-under-the-hood%2Funderstanding-ubers-share-of-driver-earnings-899d5eb733bd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20January%2C%20Uber%20%3C%2Fa%3Esaid%20that%20while%20%26quot%3Bprices%20have%20gone%20up%20significantly%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20portion%20going%20to%20Uber%20has%20remained%20largely%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyft%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frideshare-drivers-wages-robotaxi-markets-data-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGridwise's%20findings%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20good%20news%20for%20Uber%20and%20Lyft's%20bottom%20line%2C%20Green%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it's%20telling%20us%20that%20these%20companies%20are%20becoming%20much%20more%20profitable%20on%20a%20per-trip%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Uber%2C%20Lyft%2C%20or%20another%20ride-hailing%20service%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20via%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%20Signal%20at%20808-854-4501.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehere's%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eguide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-fares-rose-2025-riders-say-theyre-cutting-back-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772715601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a74fd0fd4fbd083f29760b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-fares-rose-2025-riders-say-theyre-cutting-back-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fares%20on%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20rose%2010%25%20in%202025%2C%20according%20to%20Gridwise.%20A%20majority%20of%20riders%20survyeyed%20said%20they%20are%20cutting%20back%20as%20a%20result.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-fares-rose-2025-riders-say-theyre-cutting-back-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22tit