0ballistic%20missiles%2C%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20and%20attack%20drones%20at%20Iran%2C%20using%20the%20conflict%20to%20test%20experimental%20weapons%20in%20combat%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdm.%20Brad%20Cooper%2C%20the%20head%20of%20US%20Central%20Command%2C%20confirmed%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20US%20Army%20units%20fired%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-tested-seeker-to-give-prsm-anti-ship-role-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPrecision%20Strike%20Missile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20PrSM%2C%20at%20Iranian%20targets%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20historic%20first%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ban%20unrivaled%2C%20deep-strike%20capability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PrSM%20is%20a%20short-range%20ballistic%20missile%20that%20entered%20service%20just%20over%20two%20years%20ago%20and%20can%20be%20fired%20from%20an%20M142%20High%20Mobility%20Artillery%20Rocket%20System%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-member-estonia-doubling-down-us-made-himars-ukraine-success-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHIMARS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20launcher.%20It%20is%20manufactured%20by%20the%20US%20defense%20contractor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flockheed-says-it-will-ramp-up-patriot-missile-production-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELockheed%20Martin%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20costs%20an%20estimated%20%241.6%20million%20on%20the%20low%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20said%20over%20the%20weekend%20that%20HIMARS%20had%20been%20used%20to%20strike%20Iran%2C%20though%20they%20declined%20to%20disclose%20which%20specific%20munitions%20were%20launched.%20Visuals%20of%20the%20strikes%2C%20however%2C%20strongly%20indicated%20that%20the%20PrSM%20had%20been%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PrSM's%20operational%20debut%20%26quot%3Bsignals%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20chapter%20of%20Army%20strike%20capability%2C%20with%20significantly%20greater%20reach%20and%20accuracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Patrycja%20Bazylczyk%2C%20an%20associate%20director%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies'%20Missile%20Defense%20Project%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PrSM%20is%20not%20the%20only%20new%20munition%20whose%20debut%20has%20been%20confirmed%20by%20the%20US%20military%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-us-strike-iran-preemptive-defense-chief-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmerican%20and%20Israeli%20forces%3C%2Fa%3E%20began%20striking%20Iran%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221430%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Precision%20Strike%20Missile%20(PrSM)%20fired%20from%20a%20U.S.%20Army%20M270A2%20and%20HIMARS%20at%20White%20Sands%20Missile%20Range%2C%20New%20Mexico.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8a45dfd4fbd083f2989e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22953%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Precision%20Strike%20Missile%2C%20or%20PrSM.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Christopher%20Bohn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20the%20first%20bombs%20dropped%2C%20CENTCOM%2C%20which%20oversees%20the%20military's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-weapons-used-to-attack-iran-fend-off-retaliation-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMiddle%20East%20operations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20its%20Scorpion%20Strike%20task%20force%20had%20used%20one-way%20attack%20drones%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECENTCOM%20established%20the%20task%20force%20in%20December%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20American%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-us-military-force-used-cheap-attack-drones-first-time-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eone-way%20attack%20drone%20squadron%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20region.%20Its%20combat%20debut%20over%20the%20weekend%20demonstrates%20a%20relatively%20rapid%20turnaround%20from%20fielding%20to%20operational%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20task%20force%20employs%20the%20Low-Cost%20Unmanned%20Combat%20Attack%20System%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-new-cheap-one-way-attack-drone-force-middle-east-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELUCAS%3C%2Fa%3E.%20US%20officials%20said%20that%20it%20is%20based%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-long-range-drones-hit-russian-factory-making-shahed-warheads-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIranian-made%20Shahed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20drone%20that%20has%20gained%20notoriety%20because%20of%20its%20extensive%20use%20by%20Tehran%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20by%20Russia%20in%20Ukraine.%20Each%20costs%20roughly%20%2435%2C000%20apiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20drones%20were%20originally%20an%20Iranian%20design.%20We%20took%20them%20back%20to%20America%2C%20made%20them%20better%2C%20and%20fired%20them%20right%20back%20at%20Iran%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooper%20said%20in%20a%20video%20address%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heavy%20use%20of%20cheap%20one-way%20attack%20drones%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%20has%20forced%20military%20leaders%20to%20explore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-interceptor-drones-air-defense-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emore%20cost-efficient%20air%20defense%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20that%20they%20aren't%20left%20relying%20on%20expensive%20surface-to-air%20or%20air-to-air%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBazylczyk%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bheadlines%20have%20been%20dominated%20by%20recounts%20of%20US%20forces%20using%20million-dollar%20interceptors%20against%20thousand-dollar%20drones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cost%20imbalance%20is%20shifting%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20employment%20of%20LUCAS%20drones%20against%20Iran%20demonstrates%20that%20the%20US%20is%20willing%20to%20give%20Iran%20a%20taste%20of%20their%20own%20medicine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Low-cost%20Unmanned%20Combat%20Attack%20System%20(LUCAS)%20drones%20are%20positioned%20on%20the%20tarmac%20at%20a%20base%20in%20the%20U.S.%20Central%20Command%20(CENTCOM)%20operating%20area%2C%20Nov.%2023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8a4aefd4fbd083f2989ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20LUCAS%20drones%20cost%20roughly%20%2435%2C000%20apiece.%3Cp%3EUS%20Central%20Command%20photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDan%20Rice%2C%20a%20former%20US%20Army%20artillery%20officer%20who%20served%20as%20a%20special%20advisor%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-mykhailo-fedorov-troop-shortage-awol-draft-dodging-2-million-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUkraine's%20military%20leadership%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20the%20PrSM%20and%20LUCAS%20were%20likely%20selected%20for%20their%20strikes%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Bproper%20targeting%2C%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20the%20US%20trying%20to%20show%20off%20its%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTargets%20have%20been%20planned%20for%20a%20long%20time%20in%20most%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20Rice%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20thorough%20planning%20process%20matches%20the%20right%20weapons%20with%20the%20desired%20combat%20effects.%20%26quot%3BThese%20new%20weapons%20are%20part%20of%20our%20platform%20and%20are%20doing%20their%20role.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20their%20use%20in%20combat%20gives%20the%20US%20valuable%20operational%20information%20about%20these%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military%20has%20hit%20more%20than%202%2C000%20targets%20in%20Iran%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%20Many%20of%20these%20strikes%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20by%20ground%20forces%20and%20aircraft%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D