ng%20out%20about%20private%20credit.%20What%20gives%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPE%20giant%20Blackstone%20saw%20a%20bunch%20of%20withdrawals%20from%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstones-bcred-redemptions-blue-owl-private-credit-investors-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emain%20private-credit%20fund%20for%20retail%20investors%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20redemptions%20(7.9%25%20of%20shares%2C%20totalling%20%241.7%20billion)%20actually%20exceeded%20the%20fund's%20quarterly%20limit%20of%205%25.%20Blackstone%20still%20honored%20it%2C%20but%20not%20before%20asking%20its%20executives%20to%20kick%20in%20some%20of%20their%20own%20money%20to%20help%20the%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOk%2C%20but%20what%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20private%20credit%3F%20(I%20totally%20know%2C%20but%20I'm%20asking%20for%20a%20friend.)%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt's%20when%20investors%20loan%20money%20directly%20to%20businesses%20without%20involving%20traditional%20lenders.%20While%20it%20has%20existed%20for%20decades%2C%20private%20credit's%20breakthrough%20came%20after%20banks%20had%20to%20pull%20back%20on%20lending%20following%20the%20financial%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20description%20is%20too%20simple%2C%20check%20out%20Apollo's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fd1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net%2F_78eba6f408dce0fba275cff58f32609f%2Fapollo%2Fdb%2F2224%2F22852%2Fpdf%2FPrivate%2BCredit%2B-%2BFact%2Bvs.%2BFiction.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E125-page%20slide%20deck%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20private%20credit%20that%20was%20published%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapollo-marc-rowan-want-for-christmas-define-private-credit-book-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ejust%20in%20time%20for%20Christmas%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20(Personally%2C%20I'd%20just%20take%20coal.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20Blackstone%20had%20a%20bad%20quarter%20in%20private%20credit.%20Now%20ever