2C000%20square-foot%20location%20is%20the%20first%20of%2030%20openings%20planned%20for%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20is%20doubling%20down%20on%20physical%20retail%20as%20it%20looks%20to%20reverse%20a%20trend%20of%20declining%20sales.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFresh%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20unveiling%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-bets-on-busy-families-to-return-growth-ceo-fiddelke-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20growth%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Target%20is%20set%20to%20cross%20a%20key%20retail%20milestone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20Thursday%20it%20will%20open%20its%202%2C000th%20store%20later%20this%20month%20in%20Fuquay-Varina%2C%20a%20suburb%20of%20Raleigh%2C%20North%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20we%20open%20a%20new%20Target%20store%2C%20we're%20planting%20roots%20in%20that%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20chief%20stores%20officer%20Adrienne%20Costanzo%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20148%2C000%20square-foot%20location%20is%20the%20first%20of%2030%20new%20Target%20stores%20planned%20for%20this%20year%2C%20and%20the%20company%20has%20a%20goal%20of%20300%20new%20locations%20by%202035.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20Target's%20newest%20location%20in%20North%20Carolina.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8b312d3e2f1aef36a02fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETarget%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20comparison%2C%20Walmart%20currently%20has%20more%20than%204%2C600%20stores%20and%20over%20600%20Sam's%20Club%20warehouses%20in%20the%20US.%20Costco%20has%20634%20US%20locations%20and%20another%20290%20internationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20new%20stores%2C%20Target%20says%20it%20will%20renovate%20some%20130%20existing%20locations%20this%20year%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%245%20billio