%20playbook.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20working%20on%20or%20looking%20at%20computer%20code%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699887a72237a6a8f0cd88bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI%20provides%20certain%20shortcuts%20for%20junior-level%20engineers%20and%20has%20reshaped%20daily%20tasks.%3Cp%3ENitat%20Termmee%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20is%20reshaping%20the%20work%20of%20junior%20engineers%2C%20and%20some%20worry%20they're%20missing%20out%20on%20fundamentals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBroader%20skills%20like%20problem-solving%20and%20understanding%20system%20architecture%20could%20become%20more%20valuable.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETo%20stay%20competitive%2C%20experts%20suggest%20adopting%20a%20business%20mindset%20and%20specializing%20in%20another%20area.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Ben%20Zabihi%20had%20started%20his%20career%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20his%20workday%20would%20have%20looked%20very%20different%20than%20it%20does%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20might%20have%20spent%20much%20of%20his%20time%20formatting%20code%20and%20writing%20documentation.%20Now%20Zabihi%2C%20who%20has%20been%20working%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-engineers-getting-crushed-by-ai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20software%20engineer%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20small%20New%20York%20City%20startup%20since%20December%2C%20said%20a%20good%20portion%20of%20his%20day%20is%20spent%20using%20AI%20tools%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20to%20write%20code%2C%20but%20also%20as%20a%20research%20assistant%20to%20better%20understand%20his%20industry%20and%20business%20terminology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2023-year-old%20entered%20the%20profession%20at%20a%20time%20when%20companies%20and%20workers%20are%20actively%20testing%20and%20debating%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20AI%20is%20helpful%20and%20what%20still%20requires%20a%20human%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Zabihi%20said%20that%20relying%20too%20much%20on%20AI%20at%20the%20start%20of%20his%20career%20could%20result%20in%20a%20weaker%20foundation%20for%20his%20learning%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20he%20also%20knows%20he%20has%20to%20use%20the%20technology%20and%20optimize%20his%20workflow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tasks%20that%20used%20to%20keep%20entry-level%20engineers%20busy%20might%20not%20be%20as%20important%20as%20they%20once%20were%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he's%20focusing%20on%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebigger%20picture%3A%20work%20like%20understanding%20business%20goals%2C%20system%20architecture%2C%20scaling%2C%20and%20security%20risks%2C%20which%20once%20were%20the%20domain%20of%20more%20senior%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22796d31bd-da88-488d-b67a-38809c1353b7%5C%22%3ERisk%20and%20opportunity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20recent%20grads%20see%20AI%20as%20a%20way%20to%20gain%20superpowers%20quickly%2C%20some%20industry%20veterans%20worry%20that%20the%20technology%20erodes%20a%20formative%20stage%20of%20learning%20that%20builds%20judgment%20and%20problem-solving%20skills%20%E2%80%94%20a%20gap%20that%20may%20only%20become%20clear%20as%20today's%20engineers%20advance.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhen%2036-year-old%20engineer%20Georgian%20Tutuianu%20entered%20the%20field%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20said%2095%25%20of%20the%20job%20was%20painful.%20For%20today's%20junior%20engineers%2C%20though%2C%20there%20are%20many%20shortcuts%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he's%20worried%20those%20can%20come%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20deeper%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20a%20core%20part%20of%20his%20job%20is%20managing%20codebases%20through%20pull%20requests%2C%20where%20engineers%20submit%20code%20for%20review%20before%20it's%20merged%20into%20the%20system.%20Tutuianu%20said%20he%20used%20to%20review%20around%20100%20to%20500%20lines%20of%20code%20in%20a%20pull%20request.%20Now%2C%20with%20LLMs%2C%20it's%20easily%20over%20a%20thousand%2C%20and%20he%20said%20he%20sees%20workers%20often%20add%20layers%20of%20complexity%20they%20don't%20understand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20super%20concerning%20because%20then%20you%20have%20just%20a%20pile%20of%20terribleness%20that%20you%20have%20to%20contend%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Tutuianu%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20literally%20just%20pollution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20worries%20that%20junior%20engineers%20may%20be%20outsourcing%20the%20hardest%20part%20of%20the%20job%20%E2%80%94%20wrestling%20with%20what%20they%20don't%20understand%20%E2%80%94%20to%20LLMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZabihi%20and%20Tutuianu's%20differing%20experiences%20reflect%20a%20wider%20shift%20in%20the%20industry.%20As%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20sectors%20to%20adopt%20AI%2C%20software%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-study-software-engineering-changing-ai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eengineering%20is%20being%20transformed%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20entry-level%20roles%2C%20which%20were%20once%20the%20training%20grounds%20for%20mastering%20the%20complexities%20of%20the%20job%2C%20are%20fundamentally%20changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20comes%20risk%2C%20but%20also%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221d74270b-4d7f-449b-9b36-759ada994604%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20ahead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20crystal%20ball%20to%20predict%20where%20the%20industry%20is%20headed%2C%20but%20one%20thing%20is%20clear%3A%20Junior%20developers%20are%20navigating%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-boosting-hiring-entry-level-engineers-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emurky%20employment%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20industry%20undergoes%20a%20tectonic%20shift.%20That%20means%20they'll%20need%20to%20move%20quickly%20to%20stay%20relevant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20in%20focus%20may%20also%20force%20a%20rethinking%20of%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20the%20job.%20If%20AI%20can%20handle%20much%20of%20the%20code%20itself%2C%20the%20value%20of%20an%20engineer%20might%20lie%20less%20in%20perfecting%20syntax%20and%20more%20in%20gaining%20a%20broader%20expertise%20in%20defining%20problems%20and%20architecting%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20question%20then%20is%2C%20how%20do%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20job%20and%20the%20skills%20change%3F%26quot%3B%20Matt%20Kropp%2C%20managing%20director%20and%20senior%20partner%20and%20chief%20AI%20officer%20of%20BCG%20X%2C%20the%20tech%20division%20of%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20junior%20engineer%2C%20how%20do%20you%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20meet%20those%20skills%20in%20the%20market%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeith%20Ballinger%2C%20Google's%20vice%20president%20and%20general%20manager%20of%20Developer%20%26amp%3B%20Experiences%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20beats%20doing%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20need%20to%20ask%20for%20anybody's%20permission%20to%20do%20something%20significant%20and%20meaningful%2C%26quot%3B%20Ballinger%20said.%20%26quot%3BJust%20put%20together%20a%20cool%20app%20and%20post%20it%20on%20a%20website.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBallinger%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-executive-spends-20-hours-a-week-experimenting-with-ai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20software%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20enter%20the%20field%20to%20write%20code%20in%20a%20specific%20language%20or%20framework.%20A%20developer's%20job%20is%20to%20use%20technology%20to%20solve%20problems%20and%20apply%20engineering%20techniques%2C%20he%20said.%20Great%20engineers%20have%20always%20known%20how%20to%20break%20down%20problems%20into%20smaller%20ones%2C%20and%20now%20agents%20can%20help%20handle%20the%20rest%2C%20Ballinger%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20skill%20that%20we%20can%20teach%20and%20that%20people%20can%20pick%20up%2C%20but%20now%20it's%20more%20important%20than%20ever%2C%20and%20certainly%20more%20important%20than%20memorizing%20how%20an%20API%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20Ballinger%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-boosting-hiring-entry-level-engineers-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eentry-level%20hiring%20opportunities%20shift%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mohit%20Bhende%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20engineering%20hiring%20platform%20Karat%2C%20said%20aspiring%20engineers%20should%20seek%20out%20organizations%20committed%20to%20training%20junior%20talent.%20Those%20opportunities%20may%20increasingly%20lie%20outside%20traditional%20tech%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBhende%20said%20he%20expects%20more%20talent%20to%20move%20to%20sectors%20like%20finance%20and%20healthcare%2C%20where%20AI%20adoption%20is%20slower%2C%20and%20security%20concerns%20elevate%20the%20value%20of%20human%20oversight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20CTOs%20are%20also%20increasingly%20seeking%20engineers%20who%20understand%20the%20business%20side%20of%20their%20work.%20Bhende%20said%20that%20aspiring%20engineers%20should%20prioritize%20developing%20domain%20knowledge%2C%20whether%20through%20on-the-job%20training%20or%20formal%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20you're%20graduating%20not%20just%20with%20the%20computer%20science%20degree%2C%20but%20you're%20graduating%20with%20that%2C%20plus%20a%20business%20degree%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhende%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20thinks%20%26quot%3Bthe%20jobs%20of%20the%20future%20are%20going%20to%20merge%20those%20two.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZabihi%2C%20for%20one%2C%20is%20bullish%20about%20what%20the%20rapidly%20evolving%20tech%20will%20mean%20for%20his%20career.%20He%20said%20his%20output%20is%20significantly%20higher%20because%20of%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20and%20ultimately%2C%20that's%20what%20he's%20being%20paid%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20junior%20dev%2C%20you've%20never%20gotten%20a%20better%20bang%20for%20your%20buck%2C%26quot%3B%20Zabihi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fentry-level-engineer-changes-career-development-ai-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772707861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699887a72237a6a8f0cd88bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fentry-level-engineer-changes-career-development-ai-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20has%20reshaped%20the%20work%20of%20junior%20engineers%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20could%20have%20pros%20and%20cons.%20Here's%20how%20they%20can%20still%20get%20ahead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fentry-level-engineer-changes-career-development-ai-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akshay%20and%20Shikhar%20bring%20cricket%20fever%20on%20set%20of%20Bhooth%20Bangla%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772707718000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129085961%2Cimgsize-23250.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbhooth-bangla-akshay-kumar-and-shikhar-dhawan-bring-cricket-fever-to-the-set%2Farticleshow%2F129085961.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129085961.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAfter%2014%20years%2C%20Akshay%20Kumar%20and%20Priyadarshan%20reunite%20for%20'Bhooth%20Bangla'%2C%20a%20horror-comedy%20blending%20fun%20a