er%20from%20a%20competitive%20group%20of%20options%2C%20which%20in%20this%20instance%20was%20not%20Blue%20Owl.%20Final%20negotiations%20for%20their%20equity%20deal%20are%20moving%20forward%20on%20schedule%20and%20according%20to%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Egbert%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20software%20giant%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBlackstone%20taps%20execs%20for%20cash%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224310%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blackstone%20logo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a86af4fd4fbd083f298337%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222873%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlackstone%20logo%3Cp%3ECraig%20T%20Fruchtman%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20March%202-3%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBlackstone%20is%20the%20latest%20firm%20to%20draw%20heightened%20scrutiny%20to%20the%20private%20credit%20market.%20The%20private%20equity%20giant%20was%20hit%20with%20a%20wave%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstones-bcred-redemptions-blue-owl-private-credit-investors-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eredemption%20requests%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20private%20credit%20fund%20offered%20to%20retail%20investors.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2026-03-03%2Fblackstone-senior-staff-opened-wallets-with-bcred-under-pressure%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20on%20Tuesday%20that%2C%20in%20an%20unusual%20move%2C%20the%20firm%20tapped%20more%20than%2025%20top%20executives%20to%20raise%20%24150%20million%20in%20order%20to%20meet%20the%20flood%20of%20requests.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20CNBC%2C%20Blackstone%20president%20Jon%20Gray%20said%20he%20believed%20investors%20may%20be%20motivated%20to%20withdraw%20their%20funds%20due%20to%20the%20%26quot%