20change%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20quickly.%20Here's%20the%20full%20breakdown%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F9h6mR%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Bar%20Chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F9h6mR%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed950bb6-53fa-499b-9240-bad102c45961%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3E50%25%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20much%20of%20the%20global%20robotaxi%20market%20bullish%20pundits%20think%20Tesla%20can%20grab%20in%20the%20coming%20decade.%20Cathie%20Wood's%20Ark%20Invest%20sees%20it%20earning%20that%20share%20by%202030.%20Wolfe%20Research%20also%20thinks%2050%25%20is%20attainable%2C%20but%20not%20until%202035.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6206b8d-f164-4299-a547-36b508635bf1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3E1%20million%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%202035%2C%20this%20is%20the%20number%20of%20robotaxis%20Morgan%20Stanley%20analyst%20Andrew%20Percoco%20sees%20Tesla%20hitting%20by%20then.%20That%20would%20be%20a%20precipitous%20increase%20from%20the%201%2C000%20the%20firm%20expects%20on%20roads%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026%2C%20although%20Percoco%20does%20have%20a%20neutral%20rating%20on%20the%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221042bfe9-3e71-4224-9e84-741deba7bf3b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3E%2420%20billion%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20Tesla%20has%20said%20it%20expects%20to%20spend%20on%20capex%20in%202026%2C%20more%20than%20double%20the%20%249%20billion%20spent%20the%20year%20before.%20It's%20a%20bold%20move%2C%20considering%20how%20investors%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-capex-overspending-bofa-fund-manager-survey-hartnett-2026-