-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-1-1757075398-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-1-1757075398-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496975%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20losing%20both%20parents%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20Rupam%20Sonali%20vowed%20to%20fulfil%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20dream.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20sister%2C%20Rupali%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20our%20mother%20passed%20away%2C%20it%20was%20a%20tense%20and%20uncertain%20period%20for%20us.%20As%20the%20elder%20sister%2C%20I%20felt%20responsible%2C%20but%20Roopam%20too%20carried%20herself%20with%20remarkable%20strength.%20Mum%20always%20told%20us%20to%20never%20lose%20hope%20and%20to%20find%20something%20positive%20even%20in%20the%20worst%20of%20times.%20Those%20words%20carried%20us%20through.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20pursuing%20nursing%20training.%20Financially%2C%20we%20survived%20with%20the%20small%20savings%20left%20by%20our%20parents%20and%20by%20renting%20out%20a%20few%20rooms%20in%20the%20house.%20We%20were%20careful%20not%20to%20waste%20any%20amount%20from%20life%20insurance%20because%20we%20knew%20once%20that%20money%20was%20gone%2C%20it%20would%20never%20return%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2025-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERupam%20too%20refused%20to%20compromise%20on%20her%20studies.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20very%20early%20that%20financial%20independence%20is%20the%20only%20weapon%20for%20a%20girl%20in%20such%20a%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20fund%20her%20education%2C%20she%20began%20tutoring%20students%20from%20Class%202%20to%20Class%2011.%20Every%20day%2C%20she%20woke%20at%204%20am%20to%20study%2C%20then%20travelled%2080%20kilometre